OL,5,CRED-LIGHT ON ROADS?           Q"/||?'  
OL,7, TheCGovernmentGhas scrapped the        
OL,8, environment-threatening Salisbury      
OL,9, by-pass project but given the go-ahead 
OL,10, to another bitterly opposed scheme -   
OL,11, the Birmingham Northern Relief.        
OL,13, A decision on widening theCM25Gat its  
OL,14, busiest point west of London has been  
OL,15, deferred for further studies.          
OL,17,CMinister of Transport, Gavin Strang    
OL,18, says of his roads review: "I have had  
OL,19, to make some very tough decisions."    
