OL,5,CRED-LIGHT ON ROADS?           Q"/||?'  
OL,7, Road schemes given theCgreen-lightGare:
OL,9,EGTheCBirmingham Northern Relief Road. 
OL,10,EGTheCM66 Denton-MiddletonGscheme on   
OL,11,   the outskirts of Manchester.         
OL,12,ECA13 Thames GatewayG- this includes   
OL,13,   the upgrade and operation of the A13 
OL,14,G Gtrunk corridor in east London.       
OL,15,ECA564 Derby Southern by-passG- a      
OL,16,   section of a road in Leicestershire  
OL,17,   which relieves congestion on the A50.
OL,18,ECThe A2/M2 Cobham wideningG- part of  
OL,19,   the channel tunnel rail package.     
