OL,5,CRED-LIGHT ON ROADS?           Q"/||?'  
OL,7,CConservative transport spokesman       
OL,8,CChristopher ChopeGwarns that decisions 
OL,9, to block road improvements will affect 
OL,10, the economy.                           
OL,12, "Labour's review of these schemes is a 
OL,13,Cblow to jobs and businessesGin the UK. 
OL,15, "The last Conservative government had  
OL,16, already conducted a strategic review to
OL,17, these schemes - those left in the main 
OL,18, programme areCessentialGto jobs and to 
OL,19, regeneration," he adds.                
