OL,5,CRED-LIGHT ON ROADS?           Q"/||?'  
OL,7,CFormer Tory transport ministerGand now 
OL,8, Director General of the Road Haulage   
OL,9, Association,CSteven NorrisGsays viable 
OL,10, alternatives to the road schemes about 
OL,11, to be ditched must be offered.         
OL,13, He says: "Everyone of these major plans
OL,14, were seen as solutions to today's      
OL,15, problems ofCcongestion.                
OL,17, "If a Government says, 'we are not     
OL,18, going to do these schemes' they are    
OL,19, obliged toCshow us alternatives."      
