OL,5,CRED-LIGHT ON ROADS?           Q"/||?'  
OL,7,CFriends of the EarthGbelieves the      
OL,8, Government should halt all major road  
OL,9, construction projects.                 
OL,11, Campaign directorCTony JuniperGsays:   
OL,12, "We don't need any more roads in this  
OL,13, country, what we need is challenging   
OL,14, road traffic reduction targets in law. 
OL,16, "There needs to be appropriate         
OL,17, alternative measures in the form of    
OL,18,Cpublic transport,Gbetter planning      
OL,19, decisions and changes in attitude."    
