OL,5,CRED-LIGHT ON ROADS?           Q"/||?'  
OL,7, Building more roads isCnot a solution  
OL,8, to congestion says Tony Juniper from   
OL,9, Friends of the Earth.                  
OL,11, He tells Teletext: "People understand  
OL,12, that building more roads just leads to 
OL,13, more congestion. We have toCget off    
OL,14,Cthis treadmillGof meeting demand for   
OL,15, increased road capacity.               
OL,17, "Increasing road capacity is like      
OL,18, trying toCput out a fire by pouring    
OL,19,Cpetrol on itG-Gyou make matters worse."
